episodes.title: Audiobook Janja Lalich - Take Back Your Life: Recovering from Cults and Abusive Relationships
episodes.description:
This video review features Audiobook Janja Lalich - Take Back Your Life: Recovering from Cults and Abusive Relationships

Cult victims and those who have experienced abusive relationships often suffer from fear, confusion, low self-esteem, and post-traumatic stress. 


The book can be bought on Audible at https://www.audible.com/pd/Take-Back-Your-Life-3rd-Edition-Audiobook/B0D4RCD7FC


Video Reviews, Book Trailers and Book Review Trailers are created by Essence Publishing (a subsidary of Essence Enterprises). http://essenceenterpriseus.com/
